Graham's Number
===============

## Last digits


Let's compute the last n digits of [graham's number](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graham%27s_number) with `graham_last_digits`.

```rust
use graham_number::graham_last_digits;

assert_eq!("2464195387", graham_last_digits(10))
```
